---
title: Sesame Teriyaki Chicken Traybake with Veggies & Butter Rice
description: Chicken, veggies and rice are a hearty meal, but what if we add peanut butter to a teriyaki sauce, coat the chicken, sprinkle with
sesame seeds for extra flavour and bake all of it with yummy veggies? What if then, we place it on a blanket of fluffy butter rice? We must be dreaming…or are we!

